We offer rewarding career opportunities across a wide range of clinical and
non-clinical areas across our health service and pride ourselves on providing
a work environment that is safe, satisfying, flexible, and promotes a healthy
work-life balance.

As a Metro South employee, you will benefit from a higher than standard
employer contribution to Superannuation of up to 12.75%, access to salary
packaging, flexible working arrangements and competitive salary rates with
annual incremental increases.

